### Get all courts
GET http://localhost:3000/api/courts

### Check availability
POST http://localhost:3000/api/bookings/check-availability
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startDate": "2025-10-11",
  "endDate": "2025-10-17"
}

### Create booking
POST http://localhost:3000/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "memberId": "MB-12345",
  "slots": [
    {
      "court": "Lapangan A",
      "date": "2025-10-12",
      "time": "08:00",
      "session": "day",
      "price": 75000
    }
  ],
  "totalAmount": 75000,
  "adminFee": 5000
}

### Get booking by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/bookings/{booking-id}

### Update booking
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/bookings/{booking-id}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentStatus": "paid",
  "paymentMethod": "transfer_bank"
}

### Get user by member ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/users/MB-12345